{"word":"ἐμφαγεῖν","slug":"ἐμφαγεῖν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐμφαγεῖν</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> of aor2 <el>ἐνέφαγον</el>, no <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> <el>ἐνεσθίω</el> being in use\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to eat hastily</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to eat in</i> or <i>upon</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}